        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Light-Duty Natural Gas Vehicle Parity Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Environmental Protection Agency to provide compliance and incentive values to natural gas vehicles that are at least equal to those for electric vehicles.</p>]]></text>
